1
00:00:08,948 --> 00:00:09,548
You,

2
00:00:09,787 --> 00:00:10,464
go over there.

3
00:00:10,587 --> 00:00:11,188
You,

4
00:00:11,507 --> 00:00:12,108
come here.

5
00:00:18,908 --> 00:00:19,948
Mr. Lin earlier

6
00:00:19,948 --> 00:00:21,307
was just a drop in the bucket.

7
00:00:22,948 --> 00:00:24,428
It's not too late to quit now.

8
00:00:32,096 --> 00:00:34,307
She's never on the third floor
and doesn't know rules.

9
00:00:34,307 --> 00:00:35,108
Show her the ropes.

10
00:00:35,108 --> 00:00:35,908
Okay, Mr. Tu.

11
00:00:40,908 --> 00:00:41,908
Let's go, Su Yunian.

12
00:00:57,067 --> 00:00:57,728
My apologies,

13
00:00:57,728 --> 00:00:58,307
Mr. Tang.

14
00:00:58,307 --> 00:00:59,307
Stuck with trivialities.

15
00:01:00,228 --> 00:01:00,667
Sorry.

16
00:01:00,908 --> 00:01:01,627
Pardon me.

17
00:01:02,948 --> 00:01:03,868
Sit.

18
00:01:07,468 --> 00:01:08,148
Mr. Tu,

19
00:01:09,148 --> 00:01:10,107
Mr. Tang

20
00:01:10,107 --> 00:01:12,107
has been waiting for you here
for quite some time.

21
00:01:12,387 --> 00:01:13,107
Mr. Tang...

22
00:01:14,588 --> 00:01:16,508
No big deal.

23
00:01:18,747 --> 00:01:19,667
Tonight,

24
00:01:19,747 --> 00:01:21,628
I've dismissed all mundane affairs.

25
00:01:21,628 --> 00:01:23,148
Only wish to drink

26
00:01:23,228 --> 00:01:25,068
and converse with you
at Deep In The Bustle.

27
00:01:25,348 --> 00:01:25,948
Afterwards,

28
00:01:26,187 --> 00:01:27,788
I can return to the hotel

29
00:01:27,788 --> 00:01:29,344
and quietly enjoy the fine night.

30
00:01:30,667 --> 00:01:32,027
Having entered Deep In The Bustle,

31
00:01:32,027 --> 00:01:33,187
still want a quiet night?

32
00:01:33,467 --> 00:01:34,628
That would spoil the mood.

33
00:01:35,907 --> 00:01:36,588
By the way,

34
00:01:36,907 --> 00:01:37,588
where's Lu?

35
00:01:38,187 --> 00:01:39,387
(Liu Xifan, Secretary to Deputy Governor)
He left us here

36
00:01:39,667 --> 00:01:40,588
and just took off.

37
00:01:40,588 --> 00:01:41,228
What?

38
00:01:41,788 --> 00:01:42,788
Isn't my presence enough?

39
00:01:45,148 --> 00:01:45,948
Mr. Tu,

40
00:01:45,948 --> 00:01:47,708
your words humble me too much.

41
00:01:48,027 --> 00:01:49,348
Though I

42
00:01:49,348 --> 00:01:50,628
don't have great abilities,

43
00:01:50,827 --> 00:01:51,827
I do know

44
00:01:51,827 --> 00:01:54,027
that to get to associate
with Deep In The Bustle

45
00:01:54,027 --> 00:01:55,267
is like a long drought

46
00:01:55,428 --> 00:01:56,708
finally meeting sweet rain.

47
00:01:56,708 --> 00:01:58,508
It's a heavenly blessing.

48
00:01:58,547 --> 00:02:00,107
A special envoy from the Cabinet came.

49
00:02:00,187 --> 00:02:01,228
He should meet him.

50
00:02:04,267 --> 00:02:06,148
(Tang speaks)

51
00:02:06,148 --> 00:02:07,387
(with such a pedantic air.)

52
00:02:07,708 --> 00:02:08,988
(Is he trustworthy?)

53
00:02:11,187 --> 00:02:11,628
Oh,

54
00:02:11,667 --> 00:02:12,428
Mr. Tu,

55
00:02:12,667 --> 00:02:14,387
I just mentioned to Lu

56
00:02:14,387 --> 00:02:15,987
in the elevator

57
00:02:15,987 --> 00:02:18,028
that the third floor here

58
00:02:18,028 --> 00:02:19,427
is quite particular.

59
00:02:19,427 --> 00:02:20,628
Each VIP room

60
00:02:20,628 --> 00:02:22,267
corresponds to a different rank.

61
00:02:22,587 --> 00:02:23,667
Can't just enter any room.

62
00:02:25,387 --> 00:02:26,348
Yes, Tang.

63
00:02:26,667 --> 00:02:28,387
As a deputy governor,

64
00:02:28,387 --> 00:02:30,228
you'd be in Room 333.

65
00:02:30,228 --> 00:02:31,427
But today is an exception.

66
00:02:31,547 --> 00:02:32,547
You'll have tea

67
00:02:33,028 --> 00:02:35,508
in Room 333,

68
00:02:35,707 --> 00:02:38,267
and have the meal in Room 111.

69
00:02:39,468 --> 00:02:40,547
Room 111?

70
00:02:41,468 --> 00:02:42,348
Isn't it

71
00:02:42,827 --> 00:02:45,308
only for the Cabinet and royalty?

72
00:02:49,188 --> 00:02:50,908
Who says Mr. Tang

73
00:02:51,147 --> 00:02:52,587
can't rise to the Cabinet?

74
00:02:57,888 --> 00:03:01,056
=The Glory Fades=

75
00:03:01,056 --> 00:03:03,808
=Episode 8=
(Got Slapped in the Face)

76
00:03:04,028 --> 00:03:05,107
Did you remember everything

77
00:03:05,107 --> 00:03:06,028
I told you?

78
00:03:07,308 --> 00:03:08,508
If you don't get something,

79
00:03:08,508 --> 00:03:10,068
observe and learn more.

80
00:03:10,308 --> 00:03:11,707
Or come ask me.

81
00:03:15,107 --> 00:03:16,107
Ruxue,

82
00:03:16,387 --> 00:03:17,792
do you know why Mr. Tu and Ms. Bai

83
00:03:17,792 --> 00:03:19,468
are so nice to that brat?

84
00:03:19,908 --> 00:03:21,408
I told you last time

85
00:03:21,508 --> 00:03:23,104
she is trouble.

86
00:03:23,188 --> 00:03:24,107
She's rebellious.

87
00:03:25,028 --> 00:03:26,508
Believe me now?

88
00:03:26,587 --> 00:03:27,667
Look at that brat.

89
00:03:28,068 --> 00:03:29,707
Does she look a lot like An Ruoxi

90
00:03:29,707 --> 00:03:30,867
from back in the day?

91
00:03:36,987 --> 00:03:38,688
So,

92
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:41,267
don't let her climb over your head.

93
00:03:41,867 --> 00:03:43,584
If she climbs over your head,

94
00:03:43,584 --> 00:03:45,068
we'll have no good days left.

95
00:03:47,028 --> 00:03:48,308
Did you memorize

96
00:03:48,748 --> 00:03:49,707
the info I asked you to?

97
00:03:50,028 --> 00:03:50,788
Yes.

98
00:03:50,788 --> 00:03:52,064
Yes, Ms. Bai.

99
00:03:52,308 --> 00:03:53,312
Just a deputy governor.

100
00:03:53,312 --> 00:03:54,748
I have three under me.

101
00:03:54,748 --> 00:03:56,028
You think

102
00:03:56,028 --> 00:03:57,348
I can't handle Tang Niansong?

103
00:03:58,028 --> 00:03:59,628
I can make you won't

104
00:03:59,827 --> 00:04:01,628
even shake hands with a deputy mayor.

105
00:04:02,188 --> 00:04:02,987
You believe that?

106
00:04:05,107 --> 00:04:06,068
Ms. Bai,

107
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,387
I believe it.

108
00:04:07,427 --> 00:04:08,228
I believe it.

109
00:04:11,147 --> 00:04:12,068
Mr. Tang

110
00:04:12,068 --> 00:04:13,628
will have dinner in Room 111,

111
00:04:13,908 --> 00:04:15,147
so you know what that means.

112
00:04:15,908 --> 00:04:16,948
You've seen the info.

113
00:04:18,028 --> 00:04:19,508
Mr. Tang is a man of letters.

114
00:04:19,707 --> 00:04:21,427
He quotes the classics when he speaks.

115
00:04:21,667 --> 00:04:23,227
Keep your ears peeled.

116
00:04:23,907 --> 00:04:24,668
Be cooperative.

117
00:04:25,467 --> 00:04:26,188
Got it?

118
00:04:26,188 --> 00:04:26,868
Yes.

119
00:04:36,267 --> 00:04:37,308
Yunyan, Ruxue,

120
00:04:37,988 --> 00:04:39,027
take care of Mr. Tang.

121
00:04:41,027 --> 00:04:41,868
Mr. Tang,

122
00:04:42,027 --> 00:04:43,168
heard much about you.

123
00:04:43,467 --> 00:04:44,320
Tonight,

124
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,467
it's such an honor

125
00:04:45,827 --> 00:04:47,508
to toast you.

126
00:04:47,748 --> 00:04:48,467
A toast to you.

127
00:04:48,467 --> 00:04:48,948
Here!

128
00:04:49,188 --> 00:04:49,787
I drink it all.

129
00:04:49,907 --> 00:04:50,587
Take your time.

130
00:04:52,467 --> 00:04:53,668
My name is Bai Ruxue.

131
00:04:54,027 --> 00:04:55,308
Just call me Ruxue.

132
00:04:55,308 --> 00:04:56,428
Bai Ruxue.

133
00:04:56,707 --> 00:04:57,988
A beautiful name.

134
00:04:58,227 --> 00:05:00,108
I recall a poem.

135
00:05:00,428 --> 00:05:03,347
Spring paints the town in snowy blooms.

136
00:05:03,467 --> 00:05:06,707
Amidst the mist,
the moon hangs like a hook.

137
00:05:07,068 --> 00:05:09,587
Similar scenes evoke deep emotion.

138
00:05:09,787 --> 00:05:12,384
More so when gazing from a tower high.

139
00:05:12,587 --> 00:05:14,176
No wonder I feel so familiar

140
00:05:14,176 --> 00:05:15,188
to meet you.

141
00:05:15,188 --> 00:05:16,448
It seems we're stirred

142
00:05:16,448 --> 00:05:18,308
by shared homesickness.

143
00:05:18,628 --> 00:05:19,072
Come on!

144
00:05:19,072 --> 00:05:19,748
Bottoms up!

145
00:05:20,707 --> 00:05:21,988
Mr. Tang,

146
00:05:24,508 --> 00:05:25,707
my name is Yunyan.

147
00:05:26,108 --> 00:05:27,308
'Yun' as in 'cloud',

148
00:05:27,668 --> 00:05:29,188
'yan' as in 'enchanting smile'.

149
00:05:30,068 --> 00:05:30,868
Mr. Tang,

150
00:05:31,587 --> 00:05:33,147
I have an impertinent request.

151
00:05:33,428 --> 00:05:34,587
Speak freely.

152
00:05:35,188 --> 00:05:36,707
I'd feel more comfortable

153
00:05:36,988 --> 00:05:39,308
calling you Tang.

154
00:05:39,707 --> 00:05:40,587
Well,

155
00:05:40,668 --> 00:05:42,907
that might be rather inappropriate.

156
00:05:44,827 --> 00:05:45,467
Yunyan,

157
00:05:45,948 --> 00:05:46,707
Mr. Tang is right.

158
00:05:47,227 --> 00:05:48,227
Don't call him like that.

159
00:05:48,467 --> 00:05:49,027
Right?

160
00:05:49,216 --> 00:05:50,508
Drink a penalty shot!

161
00:05:55,467 --> 00:05:56,508
Mr. Tang is right.

162
00:05:56,748 --> 00:05:58,267
I'll finish this cup.

163
00:06:04,267 --> 00:06:04,707
You,

164
00:06:04,948 --> 00:06:05,868
pour the wine.

165
00:06:08,267 --> 00:06:09,068
Come on!

166
00:06:15,707 --> 00:06:17,508
We couldn't obtain Deep In The Bustle's

167
00:06:17,508 --> 00:06:18,707
internal security footage.

168
00:06:18,707 --> 00:06:19,948
This is the footage

169
00:06:19,948 --> 00:06:21,108
from a camera near them.

170
00:06:21,668 --> 00:06:24,027
It captured the scene from that night,

171
00:06:24,027 --> 00:06:26,347
showing He Cong was being followed.

172
00:06:26,428 --> 00:06:28,068
What about this car?

173
00:06:28,707 --> 00:06:31,552
It belongs to Zhao Lu,
GM of Deep In The Bustle.

174
00:06:31,552 --> 00:06:32,147
Zhao Lu?

175
00:06:32,147 --> 00:06:32,948
He...

176
00:06:35,648 --> 00:06:37,948
It's their turf.

177
00:06:39,387 --> 00:06:40,267
Carry on.

178
00:06:41,948 --> 00:06:42,748
Mr. Tu!

179
00:06:51,027 --> 00:06:51,707
Tang,

180
00:06:52,988 --> 00:06:54,428
let's skip the pleasantries.

181
00:06:54,948 --> 00:06:55,907
Self-strength

182
00:06:56,068 --> 00:06:57,188
is the foundation.

183
00:06:57,948 --> 00:06:59,628
If we are to help you,

184
00:07:00,628 --> 00:07:01,428
we need a reason.

185
00:07:03,308 --> 00:07:04,188
Mr. Tu,

186
00:07:04,267 --> 00:07:06,428
even in a Cabinet bidding meeting,

187
00:07:06,428 --> 00:07:07,387
the other three states

188
00:07:07,387 --> 00:07:09,628
can't compete with ours.

189
00:07:16,188 --> 00:07:17,227
Mr. Tang,

190
00:07:18,227 --> 00:07:19,707
if you're truly that confident,

191
00:07:20,467 --> 00:07:21,748
let's just enjoy the meal today.

192
00:07:22,748 --> 00:07:23,387
Ah.

193
00:07:31,707 --> 00:07:33,748
The earlier surveillance clips

194
00:07:33,748 --> 00:07:34,748
prove

195
00:07:34,748 --> 00:07:36,068
it was likely Zhao Lu

196
00:07:36,068 --> 00:07:37,467
tailing He Cong's car.

197
00:07:37,707 --> 00:07:39,227
This surveillance footage is the key.

198
00:07:44,467 --> 00:07:45,948
They did this on purpose.

199
00:07:46,176 --> 00:07:47,027
Find it out.

200
00:07:47,267 --> 00:07:48,628
At any cost,

201
00:07:48,907 --> 00:07:50,068
you must find out

202
00:07:50,308 --> 00:07:52,416
what Cong did wrong that night

203
00:07:52,628 --> 00:07:54,428
to deserve such brutality from them.

204
00:07:54,948 --> 00:07:56,027
At the very least,

205
00:07:56,267 --> 00:07:58,108
Cong can't die unrequited.

206
00:07:58,387 --> 00:07:59,907
Yes, I'll go right away.

207
00:08:12,736 --> 00:08:13,787
Mr. Tang,

208
00:08:14,988 --> 00:08:17,948
the Cabinet and
Deep In The Bustle is different.

209
00:08:18,548 --> 00:08:19,680
Having you here today means

210
00:08:19,988 --> 00:08:21,188
we regard you as one of us.

211
00:08:22,227 --> 00:08:22,787
Jiasheng,

212
00:08:23,508 --> 00:08:25,147
let's not joke with our own people.

213
00:08:25,988 --> 00:08:26,787
Mr. Tang

214
00:08:26,787 --> 00:08:28,508
dares to take on this delicate task,

215
00:08:28,868 --> 00:08:30,508
he must have the skill to handle it.

216
00:08:30,508 --> 00:08:31,267
Isn't that so?

217
00:08:37,467 --> 00:08:38,148
Let's drink.

218
00:08:38,148 --> 00:08:38,467
Great!

219
00:08:38,467 --> 00:08:39,028
Let's drink!

220
00:08:39,028 --> 00:08:40,268
Come on, everyone!

221
00:08:45,308 --> 00:08:46,227
Mr. Tang,

222
00:08:46,227 --> 00:08:47,707
you're being far too humble.

223
00:08:48,227 --> 00:08:49,707
Though you're the deputy,

224
00:08:49,908 --> 00:08:51,908
even I, a mere woman, know

225
00:08:51,948 --> 00:08:53,507
you actually hold substantive power.

226
00:08:54,388 --> 00:08:56,308
Industry, finance,
environmental protection

227
00:08:56,308 --> 00:08:57,867
all fall under your jurisdiction.

228
00:08:57,867 --> 00:08:58,987
You're truly remarkable.

229
00:08:58,987 --> 00:08:59,347
Now,

230
00:08:59,347 --> 00:09:00,068
I toast you.

231
00:09:01,308 --> 00:09:02,308
Absolutely!

232
00:09:02,948 --> 00:09:04,028
He was once

233
00:09:04,028 --> 00:09:06,587
a great leader who turned the tide.

234
00:09:07,107 --> 00:09:07,987
A toast to you.

235
00:09:10,507 --> 00:09:14,068
The affairs of the world are vast
and hard to foresee;

236
00:09:14,627 --> 00:09:18,944
spring sorrows deepen,
and one sleeps alone.

237
00:09:28,428 --> 00:09:29,347
Mr. Tang,

238
00:09:30,347 --> 00:09:31,668
you're luckier than Wei Yingwu.

239
00:09:32,227 --> 00:09:33,107
Mr. Tu

240
00:09:33,268 --> 00:09:34,827
is more reliable than Li Dan.

241
00:09:35,867 --> 00:09:36,908
To jointly plan endeavors

242
00:09:37,227 --> 00:09:38,308
and achieve great things,

243
00:09:38,308 --> 00:09:39,188
so success is near.

244
00:09:40,347 --> 00:09:41,428
If you don't mind,

245
00:09:41,467 --> 00:09:42,467
I offer you a toast.

246
00:09:42,668 --> 00:09:44,480
You know Wei Yingwu's

247
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,747
'To Li Dan'.

248
00:09:46,668 --> 00:09:47,707
How impressive!

249
00:09:47,827 --> 00:09:48,707
Truly impressive!

250
00:09:49,627 --> 00:09:50,548
Mr. Tu,

251
00:09:50,627 --> 00:09:52,227
Deep In The Bustle

252
00:09:52,227 --> 00:09:54,068
lives up to its reputation indeed.

253
00:09:55,747 --> 00:09:56,627
You flatter us.

254
00:09:58,428 --> 00:09:59,308
Have you investigated?

255
00:09:59,308 --> 00:09:59,707
(I don't want Cong to die in vain.
If you behave, I'll help you avenge.)

256
00:09:59,707 --> 00:10:00,627
Who is the other party?

257
00:10:01,347 --> 00:10:02,268
I've looked into it.

258
00:10:02,268 --> 00:10:03,747
It's an overseas address,

259
00:10:03,747 --> 00:10:05,587
and it's been anonymized.

260
00:10:05,587 --> 00:10:06,627
No trail to follow.

261
00:10:09,627 --> 00:10:10,467
(I don't want Cong to die in vain.)
Mr. Mayor,

262
00:10:10,467 --> 00:10:11,908
(If you behave, I'll help you avenge.)
I truly feel for your grievance.

263
00:10:12,188 --> 00:10:13,867
Not long ago, you helped them settle

264
00:10:13,867 --> 00:10:15,227
An Ruoxi's case.

265
00:10:15,467 --> 00:10:16,507
How could they...

266
00:10:20,388 --> 00:10:21,948
Repaying kindness with enmity!

267
00:10:23,788 --> 00:10:25,867
This is blatant ingratitude!

268
00:10:34,948 --> 00:10:35,948
Yunyan,

269
00:10:36,268 --> 00:10:37,747
you have such a forthright character.

270
00:10:38,627 --> 00:10:39,308
However,

271
00:10:39,308 --> 00:10:40,747
do take better care of your health.

272
00:10:44,107 --> 00:10:44,948
Excuse me,

273
00:10:45,227 --> 00:10:46,428
I need to use the restroom.

274
00:10:54,148 --> 00:10:54,912
One of you

275
00:10:54,912 --> 00:10:56,148
goes to look after her.

276
00:10:56,428 --> 00:10:57,028
You go.

277
00:11:05,388 --> 00:11:06,188
Water.

278
00:11:07,948 --> 00:11:08,987
Water!

279
00:11:25,148 --> 00:11:26,068
Tissues.

280
00:11:27,587 --> 00:11:28,747
They're right there.

281
00:11:29,107 --> 00:11:30,107
Get them yourself.

282
00:11:35,747 --> 00:11:36,747
Su Yunian,

283
00:11:37,707 --> 00:11:38,336
don't think

284
00:11:38,336 --> 00:11:40,028
Mr. Tu let you
go to the third floor once

285
00:11:40,028 --> 00:11:41,587
means you've skyrocketed to success.

286
00:11:42,308 --> 00:11:44,428
So you can recite a few Tang poems.

287
00:11:44,908 --> 00:11:46,107
What's impressive about that?

288
00:11:47,908 --> 00:11:48,788
Yunyan,

289
00:11:49,668 --> 00:11:50,908
I've never had

290
00:11:50,908 --> 00:11:52,467
any notion of that.

291
00:11:52,668 --> 00:11:54,148
As for that poem earlier...

292
00:11:54,388 --> 00:11:56,068
No one could reply,

293
00:11:56,107 --> 00:11:56,948
and it felt awkward.

294
00:11:57,148 --> 00:11:58,867
I was just trying to fill the silence.

295
00:12:00,308 --> 00:12:02,627
I'm here to work and earn money.

296
00:12:03,068 --> 00:12:04,668
I'll go to that very floor

297
00:12:04,668 --> 00:12:05,987
the boss sends me to.

298
00:12:06,507 --> 00:12:08,227
I'll take that very position

299
00:12:08,788 --> 00:12:10,107
the boss assigns me to.

300
00:12:11,948 --> 00:12:13,987
Look at your smart mouth.

301
00:12:15,068 --> 00:12:17,668
For every word I say, you talk back ten.

302
00:12:18,068 --> 00:12:19,428
Were you raised in a barn?

303
00:12:19,467 --> 00:12:21,148
Do you even understand
respect for elders?

304
00:12:22,788 --> 00:12:24,188
I was certainly raised properly.

305
00:12:24,788 --> 00:12:25,867
I also understand

306
00:12:25,987 --> 00:12:26,948
respect for elders.

307
00:12:27,268 --> 00:12:28,107
But

308
00:12:28,388 --> 00:12:29,668
between you and me,

309
00:12:30,028 --> 00:12:31,268
is it an age difference?

310
00:12:31,428 --> 00:12:32,827
Or a status difference?

311
00:12:34,548 --> 00:12:35,827
I'm older than you.

312
00:12:36,587 --> 00:12:37,507
That makes me senior.

313
00:12:38,587 --> 00:12:40,028
I came before you,

314
00:12:40,028 --> 00:12:41,428
so my rank is higher than yours.

315
00:12:41,428 --> 00:12:42,507
That makes me superior.

316
00:12:42,867 --> 00:12:43,627
Got it?

317
00:12:44,467 --> 00:12:45,388
Now I get it.

318
00:12:45,747 --> 00:12:47,148
You're older than me,

319
00:12:47,148 --> 00:12:48,668
so I should indeed yield to you.

320
00:12:49,227 --> 00:12:49,908
Sorry.

321
00:12:50,227 --> 00:12:51,227
My mistake.

322
00:12:53,308 --> 00:12:54,107
What are you doing?

323
00:12:54,107 --> 00:12:55,428
How dare you hit me?

324
00:12:55,548 --> 00:12:57,068
Su Yunian, listen up.

325
00:12:57,587 --> 00:12:58,944
Don't think because you resemble

326
00:12:58,944 --> 00:12:59,987
An Ruoxi's looks,

327
00:12:59,987 --> 00:13:01,268
you can do whatever you want.

328
00:13:01,627 --> 00:13:03,188
This is Deep In The Bustle,

329
00:13:03,627 --> 00:13:05,268
not a college campus.

330
00:13:05,388 --> 00:13:07,028
I don't know whether I look like her,

331
00:13:07,227 --> 00:13:08,028
but

332
00:13:08,148 --> 00:13:09,467
we've never met before.

333
00:13:09,548 --> 00:13:10,308
I don't know why

334
00:13:10,308 --> 00:13:11,627
you hold a grudge against me.

335
00:13:13,347 --> 00:13:15,227
Since you took my slap,

336
00:13:15,227 --> 00:13:16,268
I'll tell you this.

337
00:13:17,308 --> 00:13:19,467
Because you look

338
00:13:19,788 --> 00:13:20,896
exactly like

339
00:13:20,896 --> 00:13:22,467
An Ruoxi.

340
00:13:23,747 --> 00:13:25,188
I'm warning you, Su Yunian.

341
00:13:25,467 --> 00:13:27,068
If you want peace,

342
00:13:27,188 --> 00:13:29,268
get out of Deep In The Bustle.

343
00:13:31,068 --> 00:13:33,148
I can guarantee your safety.

344
00:13:34,548 --> 00:13:36,428
Do you hate An Ruoxi that much?

345
00:13:43,867 --> 00:13:44,668
Mr. Tu.

346
00:13:45,308 --> 00:13:46,107
Mr...

347
00:13:50,148 --> 00:13:50,948
Does it hurt?

348
00:13:52,188 --> 00:13:52,987
It's okay.

349
00:13:53,467 --> 00:13:54,867
Thank you for your concern.

350
00:13:59,068 --> 00:14:00,148
He Cong.

351
00:14:00,388 --> 00:14:01,268
Lin Shen.

352
00:14:01,467 --> 00:14:02,308
Yunyan.

353
00:14:02,908 --> 00:14:03,908
Isn't that enough?

354
00:14:06,788 --> 00:14:07,587
Without reminder,

355
00:14:07,587 --> 00:14:08,507
I would've forgotten

356
00:14:09,507 --> 00:14:10,707
that another girl

357
00:14:11,388 --> 00:14:12,467
was supposed to be here.

358
00:14:13,188 --> 00:14:13,827
You go.

359
00:14:14,587 --> 00:14:16,188
You deliberately stopped her.

360
00:14:17,188 --> 00:14:18,227
But it's fine.

361
00:14:19,107 --> 00:14:20,388
Pain brings clarity.

362
00:14:21,388 --> 00:14:22,507
I need to get back to work.

363
00:14:35,068 --> 00:14:36,308
Did you enjoy your drinks?

364
00:14:37,587 --> 00:14:39,388
Later, I've arranged

365
00:14:39,467 --> 00:14:40,747
a private spa session for you.

366
00:14:41,747 --> 00:14:43,507
It'll be absolutely wonderful.

367
00:14:44,028 --> 00:14:44,587
Wonderful.

368
00:14:45,668 --> 00:14:46,388
Tomorrow morning,

369
00:14:46,827 --> 00:14:47,520
for our business,

370
00:14:47,908 --> 00:14:48,747
we'll go together.

371
00:14:49,148 --> 00:14:49,668
Lu,

372
00:14:50,068 --> 00:14:51,587
you can get back to your work.

373
00:14:51,587 --> 00:14:52,668
I can't keep you company.

374
00:14:52,987 --> 00:14:54,627
I'll find someone else to accompany you.

375
00:14:54,867 --> 00:14:55,827
Someone else.

376
00:14:55,948 --> 00:14:56,747
Someone else.

377
00:14:58,227 --> 00:14:59,268
Mr. Tang, good evening.

378
00:15:00,668 --> 00:15:01,668
My name is Yu Yingwan.

379
00:15:01,788 --> 00:15:03,456
Graduated
from Luosen Chinese University.

380
00:15:04,227 --> 00:15:05,188
This...

381
00:15:05,587 --> 00:15:08,827
Well, Miss Su,
who just exchanged poetry with me...

382
00:15:10,987 --> 00:15:13,068
She is Mr. Tu's new recruit.

383
00:15:16,548 --> 00:15:17,308
Yingwan.

384
00:15:17,668 --> 00:15:18,707
Lovely name.

385
00:15:18,827 --> 00:15:20,227
We'll have drinks another time.

386
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:21,747
I'll take my leave now.

387
00:15:24,107 --> 00:15:24,908
Mr. Tang,

388
00:15:25,507 --> 00:15:26,747
as the Book of Songs says,

389
00:15:27,068 --> 00:15:29,148
"Our chance encounter fulfills
my heart's desire."

390
00:15:29,388 --> 00:15:30,788
Though this is our first meeting,

391
00:15:30,788 --> 00:15:32,627
it reminds me of that verse.

392
00:15:32,627 --> 00:15:33,987
What night is tonight?

393
00:15:34,227 --> 00:15:35,627
That we share this candlelight.

394
00:15:35,908 --> 00:15:37,428
If I could converse with you,

395
00:15:37,428 --> 00:15:39,827
it would be a serendipitous encounter

396
00:15:39,827 --> 00:15:41,347
that outshines all worldly splendor.

397
00:15:41,668 --> 00:15:43,548
What a talented girl!

398
00:15:43,548 --> 00:15:44,388
Impressive knowledge.

399
00:15:44,428 --> 00:15:45,668
Indeed.

400
00:15:45,867 --> 00:15:46,388
Well,

401
00:15:46,587 --> 00:15:47,587
I'll get you some tea.

402
00:15:47,587 --> 00:15:48,227
Okay.

403
00:15:48,467 --> 00:15:49,227
This way, please.

404
00:15:49,948 --> 00:15:50,507
Lu,

405
00:15:50,548 --> 00:15:51,227
see you.

406
00:16:09,627 --> 00:16:10,827
Lu.

407
00:16:11,987 --> 00:16:13,107
You won't change?

408
00:16:13,388 --> 00:16:14,627
Haven't had enough humiliation?

409
00:16:16,388 --> 00:16:17,587
Mr. Tang

410
00:16:17,587 --> 00:16:19,668
reeks of that pretentious scholarly air.

411
00:16:20,827 --> 00:16:21,707
Lu,

412
00:16:22,308 --> 00:16:24,388
I truly have no other choice.

413
00:16:24,908 --> 00:16:26,548
I can only rely on acting shamelessly.

414
00:16:27,068 --> 00:16:28,627
I'm not like Ms. Bai.

415
00:16:28,827 --> 00:16:30,347
She is under your protection.

416
00:16:33,827 --> 00:16:35,548
Now you dare to talk to me like this?

417
00:16:36,148 --> 00:16:37,068
Aren't you

418
00:16:38,308 --> 00:16:39,388
afraid I'll devour you?

419
00:16:39,908 --> 00:16:41,068
How annoying!

420
00:16:42,028 --> 00:16:42,987
Get some rest early.

421
00:17:17,364 --> 00:17:21,038
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

422
00:17:21,337 --> 00:17:24,528
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

423
00:17:26,360 --> 00:17:29,981
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

424
00:17:30,530 --> 00:17:33,329
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

425
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:38,530
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

426
00:17:38,754 --> 00:17:42,400
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

427
00:17:43,650 --> 00:17:47,424
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

428
00:17:47,975 --> 00:17:53,090
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

429
00:17:53,794 --> 00:17:57,928
♪I feel guilty♪

430
00:17:58,498 --> 00:18:02,242
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

431
00:18:03,106 --> 00:18:06,549
♪Even in tears♪

432
00:18:07,298 --> 00:18:11,212
♪It doesn't matter♪

433
00:18:11,394 --> 00:18:15,217
♪We embrace in dreams♪

434
00:18:16,066 --> 00:18:19,712
♪I let down all my defenses♪

435
00:18:20,738 --> 00:18:24,101
♪Though the story has its end♪

436
00:18:24,866 --> 00:18:33,218
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
